{"tid":1242223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 下午考 TSA 嘅同學仔即入","createTime":"2019-06-19T03:33:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T03:41:17.000Z","uid":264099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3c43db756a992e8cb13c3b63807a2b8d872930","tid":1242223,"uid":264099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:33:23.000Z","msg":"據教師回報，你地全部做緊D 徙氣野<br />\n千萬唔好&quot;明顯地&quot;劃條bar code<br />\n教師見到一定要做野，又要逐份卷寫report，又要貼後備 bar code label 上去<br />\n考評局係完全唔會加重負擔!!!<br />\n<br />\n另，如果真係唔識做，休息一下，關心自己身心健康。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重覆：千萬唔好&quot;明顯地&quot;劃條bar code<br />\n<br />\n為教師，為自己。<br />\n做個乖學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9864d4a930b9a264c1f6eb8f6ed534717399cb1a","tid":1242223,"uid":264099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"補充：<br />\n對於做卷唔小心嘅同學，老師可憑 &quot;學號1答一號卷、學號2答二卷、學號3答三卷、學號4答一卷&quot;嘅定律搵到你出嚟關心你<br />\n如果唔想老師咁擔心，就要搵D 相關學號嘅同學仔一齊互相鼓勵，做好份卷佢。<br />\n相信同學們有相當高嘅智慧去計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1df5b69b0f7297f61a95fe88c87d012aae954d","tid":1242223,"uid":264099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"push"}]}